<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Deutsch Lernkarten</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0f0e0c;
    --surface: #1a1916;
    --card-front: #1e1d1a;
    --card-back: #16201a;
    --gold: #c9a84c;
    --gold-light: #e8c96e;
    --green: #4a9e6b;
    --red: #c0524a;
    --text: #e8e4d9;
    --text-dim: #8a8578;
    --border: #2e2c27;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 32px 16px 48px;
  }

  header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  header h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.8rem);
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  header p {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .stats-bar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }

  .stat-dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .stat-dot.total { background: var(--text-dim); }
  .stat-dot.known { background: var(--green); }
  .stat-dot.unknown { background: var(--red); }

  .stat span { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }

  /* progress bar */
  .progress-wrap {
    width: min(520px, 90vw);
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-light));
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: width 0.4s ease;
  }

  /* CARD */
  .scene {
    width: min(520px, 92vw);
    height: 320px;
    perspective: 1000px;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .card {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    transition: transform 0.55s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .card.flipped { transform: rotateY(180deg); }

  .face {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 16px;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 36px 40px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .face-front {
    background: var(--card-front);
  }

  .face-back {
    background: var(--card-back);
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
    border-color: #2a3830;
  }

  .card-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .card-word {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 6vw, 2.6rem);
    color: var(--gold-light);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .card-hint {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .card-meaning {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.25rem);
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    white-space: pre-line;
  }

  .card-example {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-style: italic;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 14px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* BUTTONS */
  .btn-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 12px 32px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .btn-known {
    background: var(--green);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .btn-unknown {
    background: var(--red);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .btn-known:hover { background: #5ab87c; transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-unknown:hover { background: #d4635a; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  .btn-nav {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .btn-nav:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }

  .nav-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .card-counter {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    min-width: 80px;
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  /* result screen */
  .result-screen {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 18px;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    width: min(520px, 92vw);
  }

  .result-screen.show { display: flex; }

  .result-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .result-numbers {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .result-num {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .result-num .big {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  }

  .result-num .label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .result-num.known .big { color: var(--green); }
  .result-num.unknown .big { color: var(--red); }

  .btn-restart {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: #0f0e0c;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 13px 40px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-restart:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }

  .flip-hint {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-top: -18px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Deutsch Lernkarten</h1>
  <p>C1 어휘 플래시카드 · 86 단어</p>
</header>

<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-dot total"></div>전체 <span id="total-count">86</span></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-dot known"></div>알았다 <span id="known-count">0</span></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-dot unknown"></div>몰랐다 <span id="unknown-count">0</span></div>
</div>

<div class="progress-wrap">
  <div class="progress-fill" id="progress-fill" style="width:0%"></div>
</div>

<!-- card -->
<div class="scene" id="scene" onclick="flipCard()">
  <div class="card" id="card">
    <div class="face face-front">
      <div class="card-label">Deutsch</div>
      <div class="card-word" id="front-word">abbauen</div>
      <div class="card-hint">클릭하여 뜻 확인</div>
    </div>
    <div class="face face-back">
      <div class="card-label">한국어</div>
      <div class="card-meaning" id="back-meaning">채굴하다</div>
      <div class="card-example" id="back-example">예문이 여기에 표시됩니다.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<p class="flip-hint">↑ 카드를 클릭하면 뒤집힙니다</p>

<div class="btn-row">
  <button class="btn btn-unknown" onclick="markCard(false)">✕ 몰랐다</button>
  <button class="btn btn-known" onclick="markCard(true)">✓ 알았다</button>
</div>

<div class="nav-row">
  <button class="btn btn-nav" onclick="prevCard()">← 이전</button>
  <div class="card-counter" id="counter">1 / 86</div>
  <button class="btn btn-nav" onclick="nextCard()">다음 →</button>
</div>

<!-- result -->
<div class="result-screen" id="result-screen">
  <div class="result-title">학습 완료!</div>
  <div class="result-numbers">
    <div class="result-num known">
      <div class="big" id="result-known">0</div>
      <div class="label">알았다</div>
    </div>
    <div class="result-num unknown">
      <div class="big" id="result-unknown">0</div>
      <div class="label">몰랐다</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <button class="btn-restart" onclick="restart()">다시 시작</button>
</div>

